<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact & FAQ</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
  
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.7.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        function showSection(section) {
            if (section === 'privacy') {
                document.getElementById('privacy-policy').style.display = 'block';
                document.getElementById('terms-conditions').style.display = 'none';
            } else {
                document.getElementById('privacy-policy').style.display = 'none';
                document.getElementById('terms-conditions').style.display = 'block';
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        .toggle-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .toggle-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            margin: 0 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .toggle-links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .last-updated {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="f-body">
    <div class="f-container">
        <div class="homeicon">
            <a href="/">
                <i class="bi bi-house-door"></i>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="f-header">
            <h1 class="head1">Privacy Policy & Terms & Conditions</h1>
            <div class="toggle-links">
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="showSection('privacy')">Privacy Policy</a> |
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="showSection('terms')">Terms & Conditions</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Privacy Policy Section (Shown by Default) -->
        <div id="privacy-policy" class="policy-section">
            <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.</p>
            <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
            <p>We may collect personal details such as your name, email address, shipping address, and payment details when you shop with us.</p>
            
            <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <p>Your information is used to process orders, provide customer support, and send important updates about our services.</p>
            
            <h3>3. Data Protection</h3>
            <p>We implement security measures to protect your personal data and do not share your information with third parties without consent.</p>
            
            <h3>4. Cookies</h3>
            <p>We use cookies to improve your browsing experience. You can control cookie settings in your browser.</p>
            
            <div class="last-updated">
                <p>Last Updated: January 10, 2025</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Terms and Conditions Section (Hidden by Default) -->
        <div id="terms-conditions" class="terms-section" style="display: none;">
            <h2>Terms & Conditions</h2>
            <p>By using our website, you agree to the following terms and conditions.</p>
            
            <h3>1. Use of Our Services</h3>
            <p>You must be at least 18 years old or have parental consent to use our services.</p>

            <h3>2. Product Availability</h3>
            <p>All products are subject to availability, and prices may change without notice.</p>

            <h3>3. Payments</h3>
            <p>We accept various payment methods, including credit/debit cards and mobile payments. Orders are processed only after payment confirmation.</p>

            <h3>4. Shipping & Returns</h3>
            <p>We offer shipping to various locations. If you're not satisfied with your purchase, you may return it under our return policy.</p>

            <h3>5. Limitation of Liability</h3>
            <p>We are not responsible for any indirect damages caused by the use of our products or services.</p>

            <div class="last-updated">
                <p>Last Updated: January 10, 2025</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
